### Get All Caretakers
GET {{baseUrl}}/caretakers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search for "pediatric"
GET {{baseUrl}}/caretakers?search=pediatric
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter by firstName
GET {{baseUrl}}/caretakers?firstName=Alice
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter by hourly rate range
GET {{baseUrl}}/caretakers?minHourlyRate=25&maxHourlyRate=30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/caretakers?page=1&limit=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sort by hourly rate (descending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/caretakers?sortBy=hourlyRate&sortOrder=DESC
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Combined search and filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/caretakers?search=care&minHourlyRate=20&sortBy=firstName&sortOrder=ASC&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search in qualifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/caretakers?search=nurse
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter by email (partial match)
GET {{baseUrl}}/caretakers?email=alice
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get specific caretaker
GET {{baseUrl}}/caretakers/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update caretaker
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/caretakers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "hourlyRate": 30.00,
  "qualifications": "Senior Licensed RN with pediatric and NICU experience"
}

### Delete caretaker
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/caretakers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
